Package: PKIplus
Version: 0.0.1.9000
Title: Public Key Infrastucture for R based on the X.509 standard, plus access functions
Authors@R: c( 
    person("Simon", "Urbanek", role = c("aut"), email ="Simon.Urbanek@r-project.org"), 
    person("Matthew", "Jones", role = c("aut", "cre"), email ="jones@nceas.ucsb.edu"))
Depends: R (>= 2.9.0), base64enc
Description: This package provides PKI functions such as verifying certificates, RSA encription and signing which can be used to build PKI infrastructure and perform cryptographic tasks. It is an extension of the PKI package, with additional methods for accessing metadata from X.509 certificates.
License: GPL-2 | GPL-3 | file LICENSE
URL: http://giithub.com/NCEAS/PKIplus
SystemRequirements: OpenSSL library
